.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, sports, western
3 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, rat
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, aconite
1. the person watching sports movies is between the owner of the frog and the person watching western movies##2
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports        | western |
| Pet           | frog   | goldfish      | rat     |
| Flower         | aconite | iris | begonia    |

