.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, argentine, chinese
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, subway, tram
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the argentine##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage    | 7up        | hot-chocolate | sprite     |
| Nationality       | polish | argentine          | chinese |
| Transport   | subway     | tram          | boat       |

