1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
3. the teacher is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Transport          | ship | motorbike | airplane |
| Job           | pilot | teacher   | scientist  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | country   | pop        |

