3 different games are played: scrabble, go, domino
There are 3 different nationalities: german, malaysian, polish
1. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the polish##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta  | almond-milk |
| Game   | scrabble  | domino    | go       |
| Nationality   | german   | polish | malaysian   |

